\begin{table}[H]
\centering
\renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
\begin{tabularx}{\textwidth}{l X X X}
\toprule
\textbf{Subsystem} & \textbf{Primary Function} & \textbf{Core Hardware} & \textbf{AI Stack} \\
\midrule
Vital32 & Continuous biometric monitoring and home automation trigger & ESP32, MAX30102, MPU6050, MLX90614, BME688, BIA circuit & LSTM, Isolation Forest, biological age model \\
\addlinespace
HollowRover & Physical response, medicine delivery, security patrol, passive barrier deterrence & D-Robotics RDK X5 (4GB), STL-19P TOF LiDAR, DW1000 UWB, MLX90640 thermal, MG996R arm & SLAM, Nav2, biomarker-triggered protocol engine, DeepFace \\
\addlinespace
SphereAI & Trimodal emotional intelligence and cognitive monitoring & Microphone, speaker, Whisper STT, OLED via rover & NLP + voice prosody + biomarker fusion classifier \\
\addlinespace
EntryGuard & 24/7 intrusion, fire, and gas detection at all entry points & PIR, MQ-2 gas, KY-026 fire, ESP32 nodes & DeepFace recognition, threat classification \\
